Table2.donot: Leave the house except for essential activities

Table2.do: Wash hands with soap and water for at least 20 seconds
Cover your cough or sneeze with a tissue
Table2.donot: Go to doctor unless you call first

Table2.do: Clean and disinfect frequently touched objects and surfaces
Maintain a safe social distance of 6 feet whenever outside of the house
Wear a cloth face covering if you go outside
